title: Space Shuttle Mission 2007
description:
Space Shuttle Mission 2007 is the newest and most exciting Space Shuttle Simulator available today, designed to provide the experience and excitement of the NASA Space Shuttle missions in extreme detail.


Included Major Service Pack 2.04 - Released August 15, 2008

This cumulative Service Pack includes STS-27, STS-122, STS-93, STS-99, STS-124, TripleHead2Go, Nvidia nView dual screen, TrackIR Pro support, iWear VR 920 stereoscopic HMD support, many improvements and some misc fixes. In addition, it includes new 3D Virtual Cockpit goodies, enhanced systems simulation and a significant increase in performance.
